            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c54f29c7-4e18-4870-b03a-62acf5328fe7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
